			    <div class="entry"><h2>With Smiths Machine, You Can Expect More.</h2>
<h3>More Precision. More Technology. More Service.</h3>
<p>From its earliest beginnings, Smiths Machine has been known for the precision it brings to the task at hand.</p>
<p>From supporting astronauts conducting research in outer space, to providing our soldiers with life-saving equipment for combat, we’re achieving the unexpected&#8211;all because of our exceptionally talented Team Members.</p>
<p>Smiths Machine owns and operates two state-of-the-art facilities in Tuscaloosa, Alabama, including over 50,000 square feet of climate-controlled work area with the capacity for over 150,000 annual machine hours.</p>
<p>With the latest technologies and equipment in CNC Milling, Turning, and Grinding coupled with CMM and Process Engineering methods, Smiths Machine is ready to help you meet every challenge along the way.</p>
<p>When you work with Smiths Machine, you can also expect a level of service that is extraordinary. And, when its all said and done, you&#8217;ll come to think of our talented team as an integral part of <strong>your</strong> team.</p>
<p><a title="Contact Us" href="/contact-us/">Contact Us</a> and let&#8217;s discuss your latest challenge.</p>
</div>
	            	            <div class="fix"></div>
	        </div><!-- /#main-page1 -->
	                    
